{"tid":1753982,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Karma -- 靈感來自香港混亂灰暗的六七月的視覺小說","createTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:33.000Z","uid":321748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cf0e79bcf632b1bf1915958eb857f8f54f682927","tid":1753982,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"七十年了，<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;是時候償還你所種下的因果了。<br />\n<br />\n以彷彿要滿溢出來的悲傷，<br />\n混亂灰暗的六、七月的香港為靈感而誕生的&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n一個反烏托邦背景之下的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.itch.zone/aW1hZ2UvNTE0ODY5LzI3MDEyMTkuanBn/original/9EgoeL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.itch.zone%2FaW1hZ2UvNTE0ODY5LzI3MDEyMTkuanBn%2Foriginal%2F9EgoeL.jpg&h=ff036c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4lAjG8b6Nj8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4lAjG8b6Nj8&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM29wwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=16a14730\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4lAjG8b6Nj8</a><br />\n<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"https://herstory.itch.io/karma\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fherstory.itch.io%2Fkarma&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM29wwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=d075b333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://herstory.itch.io/karma</a>"}]}